    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到“最伟大的联盟”！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/b21efcd1c45d57334e71b17a25de0ee7.poster.avif?t=1762949591\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/b21efcd1c45d57334e71b17a25de0ee7.webm?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/b21efcd1c45d57334e71b17a25de0ee7.mp4?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一个控制一切事物和所有人的极权主义国家。<br><br>压迫性的法律、全面监视、胆怯的民众。<br><br>你是弗兰克·施瓦兹，一位想要重获生活的丈夫和父亲。你曾经在部委拥有一份舒适的办公室工作，但当有人陷害你时，一切都变了，你失去了工作。为了防止被送进监狱，你与一位高级安全官员做了交易。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/cbc5f40268088cc6292df6cfe9d1fce7.poster.avif?t=1762949591\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/cbc5f40268088cc6292df6cfe9d1fce7.webm?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/cbc5f40268088cc6292df6cfe9d1fce7.mp4?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从现在开始，你是一名政府的间谍，伪装成房东，听从老板的命令。闯入租户的公寓，搜索非法物品，并摆脱她想摆脱的所有人。<br><br>回到部里，对同事和上级进行间谍和阴谋活动，并努力向上爬。不同的派别正在秘密地争夺部委和国家的权力。让他们相互竞争，为你带来好处。<br><br><strong>你能重新获得旧生活或创造一个更美好的生活吗？<br>你会为变革、真理而战，还是为保持一切现状而战？<br>为了得到所需的东西，你愿意牺牲谁？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/bbcd0a732a7934bdb6362f6fe3620d17.poster.avif?t=1762949591\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/bbcd0a732a7934bdb6362f6fe3620d17.webm?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/bbcd0a732a7934bdb6362f6fe3620d17.mp4?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>同时做两份工作：在公寓区和部委工作。<br></li><li>不同的政治派别正在为权力而战 - 明智地选择支持谁。 <br></li><li>完成部委的任务：传达极权主义国家的思想，操纵旗帜，并为所要宣传的思想进行鼓动。 <br></li><li>安装监控摄像头，搜查租户的公寓和官员的办公室。 <br></li><li>完成日常琐事：尽可能减少疑心。支付账单，修理公寓，满足租户的需求，而不是暴露自己。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/34a2a28ef6e1ca6ca8e8d5738759f906.poster.avif?t=1762949591\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/34a2a28ef6e1ca6ca8e8d5738759f906.webm?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570070/extras/34a2a28ef6e1ca6ca8e8d5738759f906.mp4?t=1762949591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
